data.description: Welcome to Calston Ave.! This Lancaster Property Has Plenty Of Upgrades, Extended Driveway, NEW Swamp Cooler Unit & In Ground Pool! Stepping Into This Lovely Home You'll Be Greeted With A Brick Fireplace, Natural Lighting, Spacious Kitchen With Upgraded Cabinetry, Quartz Countertops & Backsplash, Stainless Steel Sink & Wine Cooler! Updated Tile & Laminate Wood Flooring Throughout, Ceiling Fans In All Bedrooms, NEW Bathroom Toilets, NEW  Vanity & Shower Tiling. Backyard Features In Ground Pool w/ Security Fence, All Around Block Walls & Covered Patio Ready For Family Gatherings! Located Near Schools, Parks & Shopping Centers. Come Visit This Sweet Home Today!
